data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! Adorable historic home on corner lot with block fenced back yard. This 3 bed, 2 bath home has original hardwood floors. The Jack and Jill bathroom for the two guest rooms has a unique feature that is harder and harder to come by; a “Cinderella Bathtub”. Large baseboards and door trim along with the high ceilings really make each room feel extra large. Appliances stay including the gas range. More charm than the photos show, this is a must see!  *Note, the living room leather couch and chair, dining room tables/chairs, master bed, kitchen refrigerator, AND the washer and dryer stay with the property making this property basically move in ready!  So if you want to just move in and enjoy you can. Or if you want income property, you can turn this into a uber cute AirBnB/short term rental that is close to all food and shopping, this would be PERFECT and all ready to rock.
